content_request: Quelle est l'évolution du trafic data

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT 
    md.year AS year,
    md.month AS month,
    SUM(md.volume) AS total_volume
FROM 
    monthly_data AS md
GROUP BY 
    md.year, md.month
ORDER BY 
    md.year DESC, md.month DESC;
